<p style="margin-bottom:16px"><strong>Anthony Chibueze Ukwuoma</strong> is a writer and editor at <em>Ngiga Review</em>. He holds a degree in mechanical engineering from Imo State University, Owerri, Nigeria. His work appears in <em><a href="https://www.africanwriter.com/chibueze-anthony-ukwuoma-onyemeomere/">African Writer Magazine</a></em>, <em>Lolwe</em>, <em>New Black Magazine</em>, <em>Afrocritik</em>, and elsewhere.</p>
