<li>
<div><div> <a href="/blog/interviews/showing-every-day-conversation-dewaine-farria-matt-gallagher" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/default/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/Farria-Anchor.jpg?itok=7JljK8VH" width="250" height="175" alt="A photograph of Dewaine Farria with the cover to the book Revolution of All Colors" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />
</a>
</div></div><div class="views-field views-field-field-richtitle"><p class="field-content"><a href="https://www.worldliteraturetoday.org/blog/interviews/showing-every-day-conversation-dewaine-farria-matt-gallagher">Showing Up Every Day: A Conversation with Dewaine Farria
</a>
